{"tid":2164411,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 其實係咪要重新審視「未成年性交/色情」嘅凖則？","createTime":"2020-08-19T07:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T17:20:33.000Z","uid":129959,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d713d80258ed31c87587dc06d03f5505704faeb1","tid":2164411,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"非法律專家但認真post<br />\n<br />\n隨住資訊越來越普及，後生越來越早熟就一定。<br />\n一個90後同老竇老母個一輩嘅性觀念已經完全唔同。<br />\n大把00後form 1 form2已經破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，只不過雙方自願又無流出，所以先唔係咁多人被告衰十一。<br />\n<br />\n今日一起身見到個流出post，大把80/90後去到成30歲都未玩到咁。<br />\n其實係咪我地美其名保護青少年，但實質上剝奪左佢哋享受性愛嘅權利/自由？法例上係咪應該調低衰十一嘅年齡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話法例係保障青少年免於被成年人侵犯，所以法例上會唔會可以有一個空間，係容許同齡嘅青少年合法地性愛，但係同時間，就不容許成年人同青少年性愛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />與其用法例保護，不如用正確嘅性教育去保護青少年，呢方面香港不嬲都好貧乏。<br />\n<br />\n同埋好似今日個流出post，好多人話個男仔衰十一，但在我而言，咁嘅諗法係父權思想+社會嘅副產品，好似講到女仔無資格享受性愛，同時間將所有責任推向男方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96e71a00c16f7561221243b64eb9d91200bb56f","tid":2164411,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bc4cee48f79df84b222536de83c07050001ac0","tid":2164411,"uid":127425,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:45:59.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n應該降低合法性交年齡至12歲"},{"pid":"9155a2b68e645657046292d26b5e8b55448988ce","tid":2164411,"uid":275787,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:49:25.000Z","msg":"重點係<br />\n<br />\n小朋友閱歷少<br />\n容易被年紀大啲嘅人呃 （你都可以話廿幾歲嘅都會俾人呃 但係少好多）<br />\n而且會造成心理創傷<br />\n對佢性格都會有影響 甚至會衍生精神病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心智成熟同閱歷係兩樣嘢嚟"},{"pid":"3c34293c5b957c576a9af96909341d3375a1e79a","tid":2164411,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9bc4cee48f79df84b222536de83c07050001ac0","tid":2164411,"uid":127425,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:45:59.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n應該降低合法性交年齡至12歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745bfc70ddfadd38fc1007a9b0b899461c2aef56","tid":2164411,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"15b9b415142787a14563dd6560c6751fc58c0d14","tid":2164411,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"判幾重好多睇雙方年齡差距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a6204da6b3290a5b89048759cc9ce6ab37bc3b","tid":2164411,"uid":6777,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"乜生理發育會因為時代改變而改變架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6844162af0673ab4d5260436c1c8654d3659d07","tid":2164411,"uid":43717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0a6204da6b3290a5b89048759cc9ce6ab37bc3b","tid":2164411,"uid":6777,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"乜生理發育會因為時代改變而改變架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"12238dd26935703e325f7e16ced925d6b9c66e6b","tid":2164411,"uid":46587,"like":1,"